QuestData.Title: Landgrab
QuestData.Description: The Horde's Axebite Marines are all up in my precious, precious beach.$B$B<The Lieutenant points north, along the shore.>$B$BKill them.
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay 12 Axebite Marines on the Twilight Shores in Twilight Highlands.
QuestData.RewardText: Dead? By the dozen?$B$BIt's a start, $c. It's a start.
